Click Path Game to do automatically:
To enable telemetry in dirt 2, open C:\Users\username\Documents\My Games\DirtShowdown\hardwaresettings\hardware_settings_config.xml, find the line
<motion enabled="true" extradata="1" ip="127.0.0.1" port="20777" delay="1" >
and set udp enabled to true. Port should be 20777
